text: Falsamblesthis candicans is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Gounelle in 1910. It is known from Ecuador.BioLib.cz - Falsamblesthis candicans. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Forsteriini Category:Beetles described in 1910
